        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "7 IN 1 SURVIVAL KIT: Survival tools include thermometer (Celsius and Fahrenheit), signal mirror, compass, short range safety whistle, LED flashlight, 5x magnifier and small storage compartment",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Use the built in whistle to signal your location to friends and search and rescue when in need; the built-in storage compartment is excellent for storing waterproof matches or medication",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Durable ABS plastic body comes in a bright orange or forest green color which improves visibility or helps blend with your existing gear depending on your color choice",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Includes lanyard strap so you can easily hang it around your neck, on your belt or your backpack",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Teach kids about outdoor camping and hiking safety; This multi-use whistle is the start to good preparation and essential outdoor safety",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Compact survival kit is great for kids to include with their hiking and camping gear; Learn the basics of the great out doors",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "catalog",
            "asin": "B074JXT2SF",
            "raw_value": true
        },
        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "This is a simple to use 7 in 1 waterproof survival multi-purpose whistle.<br/><br/>With camping season just around the corner, it's a great time to teach your children the basic camping and survival skills that have been handed down to you by your parents, their parents, and of course the Boy Scouts. <br/><br/>This multi-use whistle is the start to good preparation and essential outdoor safety. Each whistle features 7 functions - whistle, magnifier, flashlight, storage container, compass, thermometer and a signaling mirror. The plastic body is a bright orange color to improve visibility and it comes with a lanyard so you can easily hang it around your neck, on your belt or your backpack. Make sure to grab a few of these before your next camping trip.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "catalog",
